description=Autonomous AI agent-as-OS for Android. v0.4.4: offline Thai-capable STT (whisper.cpp), bg → Telegram completion notifications, audit-driven hardening (CleanupGuard / UTF-8 / plan auto-approve / RpcDispatcher), vendor-binder shim (camera + GPS + telephony) + streaming event bus, bg persistence + checkpoint resume, PCM record / playback / TTS, ambient-audio heuristic labels. Installs peko-agent + peko-llm-daemon + tesseract + whisper-cli into /system/bin with boot-time services and PekoOverlay + PekoSmsShim priv-apps. Multi-provider cloud chain, full autonomy stack, web UI on :8080, Telegram bot. Verified end-to-end on OnePlus 6T (fajita) / arm64 / LineageOS 20.
updateJson=
